    <h1>20260416 - LapuLapu Team Direction and Execution</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h2 local-id=3D"25e42c8101db" id=3D"id-20260416-LapuLapuTeamDirecti=
onandExecution-ExecutiveAgenda(30minutes)=E2=80=94TeamDirection&amp;Executi=
on(withBirgerFjaellman)">Executive Agenda (30 minutes) =E2=80=94 Team Direc=
tion &amp; Execution (with Birger Fjaellman )</h2>
<p local-id=3D"1d9d05d376e6"><strong>Objective:</strong> Align on <em>direc=
tion</em>, confirm <em>execution path</em>, and leave with <em>3=E2=80=935 =
explicit decisions/asks</em> that unblock delivery this week.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"5c54f34e-d87d-40de-aba0-63f5194b0d44">
<ul local-id=3D"0c2761b5-e872-42ca-bb2a-2ff104449ee9">
<li local-id=3D"66cec025-7f0d-496e-8864-d30a0109b1b8">
<p local-id=3D"ff61627b837c">Where do <strong>New Relic-&gt;Moogsoft Alerts=
/Incidents</strong> go? Can we find the setting that registers the support =
team?</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"90f9ed58-e0ca-4175-9cfe-6635f6fcc0d8">
<p local-id=3D"0856fd509785">Working on <strong>Non-Prod Monitoring workloa=
d</strong>. Next steps - Alert response workflow (Sangram/Rupesh/Rae), foll=
owed by Environment spin-up/down and Rapid Recovery</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2396d95f-6ee7-4ac6-95cc-1a46da769508">
<p local-id=3D"e1fe3a205022"><strong>Capacity monitoring setup</strong> - C=
onfirm the settings (Balaji)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c72005b5-cad9-469d-a5f0-c44d4fd19b8c">
<p local-id=3D"bbf0db0df422"><strong>Side Quest Transfer Ownership for Serv=
erF</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"52c29b30-f33a-43b0-8f78-d91fbb98f4e5">
<li local-id=3D"73305ddd-8bc1-4037-a47f-bff4a7710545">
<p local-id=3D"e6d76c4803d5">File Share: Jonan(GOCC), JB Villegas(GAM) task=
ed to set up a Fileshare management service</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"51a92413-624e-495b-8c97-406d0d0dca5b">
<p local-id=3D"db603a6cfd15">File transfer: Joan Lee (GBO, MW), JB Villegas=
(GAM) has MFT team to work on FTP and MFT activities</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"a3a156c9-fc45-4f26-be2d-5b17e422a639">
<p local-id=3D"3da59f9cb533"><strong>Side Quest Patching - Weekday</strong>=
</p>
<ul local-id=3D"09ba7970-96ef-4daf-ac69-0f06088a793d">
<li local-id=3D"c325160e-b2d8-465e-96a0-5ce7ef5ba939">
<p local-id=3D"e0bc200dc23c">Pull all systems that are not on the main list=
 (David)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"1e275b03-0592-4190-9d18-bac89de3d6ab">
<p local-id=3D"ac61647451fd"><strong>Side Quest</strong> <strong>Setup Goph=
er</strong> to annoy ETS Japan - Keni, Birger (Nakatsu)</p>
<ul local-id=3D"928b477c-14e9-4957-bcb5-7c878de7169d">
<li local-id=3D"45261ca3-6bef-4b92-8b24-e18116c78659">
<p local-id=3D"d06e20db8d86">Teams, email 2x / day</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"55d3c21c-bda9-4d86-b727-d58c8712eb24">
<p local-id=3D"5c7ebfd097ab">Add manager after 24 hours</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"db8f5061-4388-4c25-9ef3-ec1b311e4e3a">
<p local-id=3D"d41d714b04ff"><strong>Orphaned assets list</strong> burn it =
down by category and start with servers (Yegor)</p></li>
</ul>
    </div>
